{"tid":1773213,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（入嚟睇睇) 3招將淺藍變淺黃，淺黃變深黃！","createTime":"2019-12-07T09:53:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T10:39:03.000Z","uid":301388,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"45d64df13fbd63b89452bdc5f0c4b4298918c2e5","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"是咁的，大學提早完sem之後我番咗屋企住。由於屋企比較多親戚，成日要同埋啲三姑六婆食飯，好彩當中深藍嘅唔多，不過好多都係淺藍/黃，於是我就試下向佢地宣揚下革命思想 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，暫時都幾work，至少我老母由淺藍變咗宜家識得準時轉台睇ViuTV/有線新聞，一睇新聞見到啲高官就賤狗前賤狗後咁屌。<br />\n戴番個頭盔先，講明係將淺藍變淺黃，所以深藍廢老真係無得救，唯有望佢地快啲死。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好，入正題，宣傳/傳播媒介主要可以分做3個層次，由最低到最高分別係：<br />\n1. 知曉層次<br />\n2. 態度層次<br />\n3. 行動層次<br />\n而達到以上3個層次，分別可以用以下嘅方法：<br />\n1. 說之以理<br />\n2. 動之以情<br />\n3. 誘之以利<br />\n<br />\n咁即係點？宜家就逐樣講下: (最底有懶人包）<br />\n1. 知曉層次 - 說之以理<br />\n呢度係講緊控制淺藍/黃嘅資訊來源，同埋用最<span style=\"color: gold;\">簡單直接</span>嘅方法俾佢地接觸對場運動有利嘅資訊。其實控制資訊來源呢樣嘢共產黨喺大陸一路都做緊，我地只不過係以其人之道還治其人之身。一般廢中/老都<span style=\"color: gold;\">無乜耐性聽咁多理論</span>，所以說服佢地嘅時候千祈唔好浪費時間講道理，因為佢地覺得道理佢地最熟，你班後生唔會識嘢。同佢地講嘢要用資訊/新聞開始先，跟住先再繼續解釋。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">例子：</span></strong><br />\n當你見到老母喺屋企長開83台新聞，<br />\n不要說：&ldquo;唔好睇無綫啦，佢地係政府喉舌嚟㗎，傳媒應該獨立公平客觀㗎嘛！&rdquo;<br />\n試著說：&ldquo;記唔記得之前嗰個趙家賢俾人咬耳仔幾恐怖呀，呢個台話佢隻耳仔自己跌路嚟㗎，唔好睇啦！&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n2. 態度層次 - 動之以情<br />\n呢層就難少少，首先要把握好呢班淺藍/黃嘅特徵。我接觸嘅呢班人多數都係50-60歲嘅中老年人，佢地有幾個共同特點。第一，<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">左膠不過大愛</span></span>，即係對暴力反感，不過見到啲後生仔受傷又會心痛。第二就係覺得自己看透世事，食鹽多過你食米，又<span style=\"color: pink;\">要你尊重佢地</span>。所以同佢地講嘢<span style=\"color: gold;\">唔需要硬碰</span>，唔好辣著佢地，<span style=\"color: orange;\">佢地辣著咗就乜都唔會聽</span>。仲有，唔需要迫佢地認同曬五大訴求<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">住</span> (雖然五大訴求缺一不可)，可以從獨立調查同雙真普選入手，令佢地覺得你係一個講道理，有商有量嘅人，再慢慢潛移默化佢地。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">例子：</span></strong><br />\n三姑六婆：&ldquo;哇班後生仔由掟汽油彈由爆玻璃，咁暴力都有嘅！&rdquo;<br />\n不要說：&ldquo;係政府制度暴力在先！佢地迫不得已先要咁㗎咋！&rdquo;<br />\n試著說：&ldquo;其實我都好反對暴力㗎，所以我地要用啲有效嘅方法從根源止暴，政府用嗰幾招用咗半年都無用，就知唔work啦！仲有，我最憎暴力㗎啦，所以我覺得用暴力嘅人要拉曬去坐監，不過宜家好似有班人(唔好講警察住，佢地自然會問 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) 使用完暴力之後仲榮華富貴，加官晉爵喎，唉，所以真係鄧班後生唔抵呀，個個上完街就要坐十年八年...&rdquo;<br />\n類似嘅論調其實石永泰講過，我俾過啲淺藍/黃睇呢條片，so far 無人駁到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TCeQLirtFUs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTCeQLirtFUs&d=dMuVdPjJf30Qxtl2jkPsRJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=ba634015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TCeQLirtFUs</a><br />\n<br />\n3. 行動層次 - 誘之以利<br />\n記住，大部分&ldquo;中立&rdquo;/&ldquo;淺藍&rdquo;嘅人都係<span style=\"color: gold;\">利益行先、唯利是圖</span>嘅人。有佢地著數嘅嘢佢地就會做，所以，得到佢地嘅支持後，要佢地付諸行動，就要俾佢地知道行出嚟有佢地著數。既然對家成日出$800 一日包飯盒請人，我地就要傳播一種意識，就係只要佢地肯企嚟，革命成功之後唔單止有$800，股票仲會大賺。我記得之前觀塘區有份文宣（好似叫觀點？) 做得幾好，寫明抗爭以嚟嘅幾個月恆指都係升嘅，每次有衝突/政府讓步之後個市都企穩，有埋圖表，睇開股市嗰啲中/老年人對呢啲最敏感。仲有，可以同佢地講下宜家經濟攬炒又唔係佢地蝕，係大財團蝕咋嘛，不過如果政府唔繼續打壓，中美傾得成，到時就係佢地有著數喎，<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">要知道，蝕無佢地份，賺就有佢地份，呢個concept對佢地嚟講真係好撚吸引。</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">例子：</span></strong><br />\n淺藍/黃親戚：&ldquo;唉幾時先完啊，日日喺度燒舖掟嘢搞到市道差曬！&rdquo;<br />\n不要說：&ldquo;係政府 xxxxxx (下刪幾百字) 所以啲人先掟嘢咋！&rdquo;<br />\n試著說：&ldquo;唉，如果政府早啲讓步，成立獨立調查委員會，美國咪肯同中國囉，中美傾得成咁啲單咪自然番嚟囉...&quot; （學埋佢地種無奈tone)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">tl;dr? 懶人包喺度：</span><br />\n1. 控制佢地嘅<span style=\"color: gold;\">資訊來源</span>，用多啲<span style=\"color: gold;\">簡單直接</span>嘅比較說服佢地，唔好咁多理論。<br />\n2. 唔好硬碰，以退為進，唔需要迫佢地認同曬所有嘢，只需要佢地情感上企我地呢邊，<span style=\"color: gold;\">同情抗爭者，討厭當權者</span>。<br />\n3. 用<span style=\"color: gold;\">錢</span>利誘，用一個<span style=\"color: gold;\">長遠</span>嘅角度(佢地最鍾意) 俾佢地睇度運動成功之後會有幾好。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">最後，128 維園見！可以嘅話就帶曬全家出嚟</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e3c7bb12b480af7f7a3a9a0670cd582d7899d1","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:54:38.000Z","msg":"128"},{"pid":"8bc6cb6198c9852e2c2d4d39431e76de79d7fd76","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:54:50.000Z","msg":"128 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1555b9ce739216e5a33bee5485e7c07633b0d9d","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔郁 <br />\n128 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e0ca94b154e15dcedaad13d8f8adc707b12ab6e","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:57:14.000Z","msg":"128128128128 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ace1a56ec8ac7aefc4f10e428e63a5d04083a6","tid":1773213,"uid":258345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T09:58:18.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"8f25da1e6176b4f6788a13ae3783c2324d35ca8c","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Um74DWr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUm74DWr.jpg&h=28dc5195&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9eb073b12a168713679f4d9eefcb514a9eebb082","tid":1773213,"uid":218811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:01:31.000Z","msg":"有用po推<br />\n身邊啲中/老年人都係比較易接受獨立調查呢個point"},{"pid":"33bc3874c8dfab35c7334d8709c57f3344a4164f","tid":1773213,"uid":311154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:03:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70ed157a5e33af1618dcc831612825b360d24ccb","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:08:34.000Z","msg":"P牌求幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc84805e364f431774d843198b1e83904acf46bd","tid":1773213,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:09:02.000Z","msg":"政治嘅目的就係令本來唔支持我哋嘅人支持我哋，向住依個方向行一定冇死。"},{"pid":"74c1e456c71bf9748ceac962b40867036504037e","tid":1773213,"uid":32655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:09:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03baa49608aa39173247b926748467b219de08bc","tid":1773213,"uid":35231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"將佢至親代入"},{"pid":"3fd21b0fb8124bb93d932864d6ab68a7b6b25d50","tid":1773213,"uid":140538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:10:42.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭王HK Apocalypse 梁樂聞無去過示威!搵黃色經濟圈水原來真藍絲,俾咗資料小心!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1773154\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1773154</a>"},{"pid":"56f8bbbfa3cc85a7fa8fe10de567f166301c47df","tid":1773213,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:11:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"32f54da14cb94a72828684bc5f67bfdb9f00cfe0","tid":1773213,"uid":73619,"like"