"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:19:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52d5d4e45a415994e7b6461fd3f65ed8a993c0c8","tid":1773213,"uid":266273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:20:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6dbf02278de8e8625b24a06d7ccd03901d05b873","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"03baa49608aa39173247b926748467b219de08bc","tid":1773213,"uid":35231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:10:39.000Z","msg":"將佢至親代入"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:21:01.000Z","msg":"啱呀，我俾咗嗰張 &ldquo;他叫周梓樂，他只是恰巧不是你家兒子&rdquo; 我老母睇，佢呆咗幾秒，之後講咗句 &ldquo;唉，無陰公...&rdquo;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d2066167d51e468404cd28840dc82da7f8d9c60","tid":1773213,"uid":301388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-07T10:39:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oos0WVR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foos0WVR.jpg&h=9049c902&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}